This paper deals with natural language processing (NLP) and machine translation (MT) tasks, which are typically categorized under cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also involves the use of machine learning techniques, which falls under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning). The authors also mention the use of neural networks, which is a subfield of cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing). Finally, the paper involves the evaluation of MT systems, which can be categorized under cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) as it involves the comparison of machine-generated text with human-generated text.
